column1: Counsel appearing for  the Accused -Appellant informs that  she
has  gone  through  the  appeal  brief very  carefully  and  there  is  no  merit  in

this case  to  proceed  the 
appeal  to  challenge  the  conviction.  Therefore  she

wish es  to  withdraw  the 
appeal  against  the  conviction  and  further,  she

makes  submissions 
to  back date  the  sentence  from  the  date  of conviction
